
WalT platform control tool
-> management of WalT platform devices

Usage:
    walt device SUBCOMMAND [args...]

Help about a given subcommand:
    walt device SUBCOMMAND --help

Help about WalT in general:
    walt help show

Sub-commands:
    show    print details about devices involved in the platform
    shell   run an interactive ssh session to a device
    tree    print the network structure of the platform
    rescan  rescan the network devices involved in the platform
    rename  rename a device
    config  get or set devices configuration
    ping    check that a device is reachable on WalT network
    forget  let the WalT system forget about an obsolete device
    expose  expose a network port of a device on the local machine
